kt f\u00e5 uheldige konsekvenser.", "Nasjonalt folkehelseinstitutt har nylig laget en fin brosjyre som kan lastes ned til foreldre om barnets sosiale utvikling de tre f\u00f8rste leve\u00e5rene.", "Glad i debatt? Da er du kanskje interessert i mer debatt? Tenk litt over det: Er du snill fordi du forventer noe tilbake?"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "fea3f09879ee79c713187a864c65f11d23389a6492c5cdda9bba48e35836f146"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-07-30T15:37:03.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Jorunn Lervik minner oss p\u00e5 at smarttelefonen ikke m\u00e5 ta fokus vekk fra minstemann"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13106400.ece/xnj1li/ALTERNATES/w980-default/file6ntdyxu9co7102fko3bp.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/781ad1117e0bf3fe8f8c37269fe05c1d8e5be5ba.jpg?59651d26"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Ikke glem lille meg! -adressa.no", "Avhengig av omsorgspersoner", "Samspill"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "781ad1117e0bf3fe8f8c37269fe05c1d8e5be5ba"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Barn", "Familie", "mobil"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Barn,Familie,mobil"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barn", "lille barnet"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "familie"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "jorunn lervik"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13106400.ece/xnj1li/ALTERNATES/w980-default/file6ntdyxu9co7102fko3bp.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field